            {
               "text": "### Imágenes de Ashmolean\n\nEstas imágenes tienen derechos de autor de Ashmolean y se permite su uso de acuerdo con la licencia determinada por ellos.\n\nPara visualizar todas las imágenes, use las flechas izquierda y derecha en el siguiente slide.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 4</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgEA\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgEA', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Fragmento del épico de <i>Enmerkar y el Lord de Aratta</i>. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('434e68bc-6ee5-4b45-8692-beb26bd9da7f'); return false;\"><i>Ashmolean Image Library</i></a>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">2 / 4</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgHarappaW\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgHarappaW', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Sello de Harappa. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('1696d647-d450-44e3-9067-18aac69bce3d'); return false;\"><i>Ashmolean Museum Oxford, 11/30/2024</i></a>). Compartido sob la licencia <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/\" target=\"_blank\">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">3 / 4</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgS\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgS', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Estatuillas de la Sexta Dinastía. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('f3b5c752-03d2-446d-b398-2c7f3ad4c2ee'); return false;\"><i>Ashmolean Image Library, 01/02/2025</i></a>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">4 / 4</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgKL\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgKL', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Lista de los Reyes Sumerios. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('4d0b579d-57af-45e1-87b0-d402dd778968'); return false;\"><i>Ashmolean Image Library, 02/01/2024</i></a>).</div></div><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "### Image Descriptions\n- **Slide 1 / 4**: Fragmento del épico de *Enmerkar y el Lord de Aratta*. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (*Ashmolean Image Library*).\n- **Slide 2 / 4**: Sello de Harappa. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (*Ashmolean Museum Oxford, 11/30/2024*). Compartido sob la licencia Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0).\n- **Slide 3 / 4**: Estatuillas de la Sexta Dinastía. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (*Ashmolean Image Library, 01/02/2025*).\n- **Slide 4 / 4**: Lista de los Reyes Sumerios. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (*Ashmolean Image Library, 02/01/2024*).",
